name: One party and four public toilets ´´´´
description:
It's been three days in a row, luckily someone bought some food to recharge our batteries, I don't think I've ever sweated this much. I can't get out of this toilet, the pleasure is too intense and I don't know if I'll ever go to a party like this again.
If the toilet was bigger I have no doubt that there would be more of us in here. Somehow we are more already, you are watching.
